In the ESP-Matter Zap workflow, Read/Write callbacks for custom data are typically registered via the ESP-Matter API (like `esp_matter_attribute_read_callback`) in your `app_main.cpp`, rather than being defined in `CodeDrivenCallback.h`. `CodeDrivenCallback.h` is primarily for lifecycle events (like initialization).

